lost_kingdom.name: Lost Kingdom
lost_kingdom.info: Deep in the forgotten lands lies a once-great kingdom
dialogs: The Lost Kingdom calls to you, brave hero.
lost_kingdom.accept: I will explore the lost kingdom!

shadow_invasion.name: Shadow Invasion
shadow_invasion.info: Dark forces are invading from the shadow realm
dialogs: The shadows grow stronger each day.

corrupted_lands.name: Corrupted Lands
corrupted_lands.info: The corruption spreads across the realm
dialogs: The land itself cries out in pain.

ancient_evil.name: Ancient Evil
dialogs: An evil older than time itself stirs.

heroes_alliance.name: Heroes Alliance
heroes_alliance.info: Unite the greatest heroes of the realm
dialogs: We need the mightiest heroes united.

dragon_trials.name: Dragon Trials
dialogs: The dragons test only the worthy.

dragon_heart.name: Dragon Heart
dialogs: The Dragon Heart holds immense power.

dragon_pact.name: Dragon Pact
dragon_pact.info: Form a pact with the ancient dragons
dialogs: The dragons offer their alliance.

sky_fortress.name: Sky Fortress
dialogs: The Sky Fortress threatens all below.

chaos_storm.name: Chaos Storm
dialogs: Chaos threatens to tear reality apart.

dimensional_rift.name: Dimensional Rift
dialogs: Rifts are tearing our world apart.

realm_defenders.name: Realm Defenders
realm_defenders.info: Rally the defenders of the realm
dialogs: Our realm needs its defenders now.

realm_portal.name: Realm Portal
dialogs: The portal must be secured.

void_invasion.name: Void Invasion
void_invasion.info: Stop the invasion from the void
dialogs: The void consumes everything.

final_battle.name: Final Battle
dialogs: This is the final confrontation.

gathering_storm.name: Gathering Storm
dialogs: A storm unlike any other approaches.

last_stand.name: Last Stand
dialogs: This is our last chance.

new_era.name: New Era
new_era.info: Begin a new era of peace
dialogs: A new age dawns.
new_era.decline: I belong to the old ways.

sacrifice_of_heroes.name: Sacrifice of Heroes
sacrifice_of_heroes.info: Honor the sacrifice of fallen heroes
dialogs: Heroes gave everything for this moment.

eternal_guardian.name: Eternal Guardian
dialogs: The realm needs an eternal protector.

legacy_of_heroes.name: Legacy of Heroes
dialogs: Heroes must never be forgotten.

restoration.name: Restoration
restoration.info: Restore the world to its former glory
dialogs: The world can be healed.
The dark path offers power but at a cost.
The path of light is difficult but righteous.

shadow_cult.name: Shadow Cult
shadow_cult.info: Infiltrate and destroy the shadow cult
dialogs: The shadow cult grows stronger.

forbidden_ritual.name: Forbidden Ritual
dialogs: A dark ritual threatens the realm.
forbidden_ritual.decline: I don't meddle with dark magic.

dark_fortress.name: Dark Fortress
dialogs: The dark fortress looms ahead.
